  "name": "RPlog_Guest_of_the_Empire_part_4",
  "title": "Guest of the Empire, Part IV",
  "summary": "Worn to catatonia in her Broadsword cell, the captured Chyleni pilot Kyrin Sh'vani faces ISB Commissar Korynn Fleming's most calculated cruelty. Aided by the computer specialist Roth, Fleming stages a wholly simulated holo-display of two Star Destroyers poised to bombard her homeworld Chylene, threatening to exterminate her people and amputate her wings unless she surrenders the New Republic's blockade-running intelligence. When Kyrin defiantly begs him to spare her people and leave only her wings, Fleming pretends to stand the fleet down, then has her strung up by ropes and brings in a surgical kit. Without anesthetic, he carves into the joint of her left wing, crushing an artery and beginning to sever the tendons, until the agony and terror finally break her. Sobbing, Kyrin pours out everything she knows, then whispers a plea to be killed; Fleming coldly refuses, knocks her unconscious, and begins methodically repairing the wound he inflicted.",
